OL,3,EWHAT HAPPENED THIS YEAR:GPC ```````````
OL,4,BAnyone who visited the Electronic      
OL,5,BEntertainment Expo in Atlanta this     
OL,6,Bsummer came away with one word on their
OL,7,Blips: "3DFX".                          
OL,8,B                                       
OL,9,FThough technically it isn't a word, but
OL,10,Fa number and three letters, this year  
OL,11,Fhas been the year of 3DFX, and 3D      
OL,12,Faccelerator cards.                     
OL,14,BThis time next year every PC game will 
OL,15,Beither be compatible with, or require  
OL,16,Bas standard, a 3D card. Practically    
OL,17,Bevery 3D PC game in the last six months
OL,18,Bhas featured 3D enhancements. Except   
OL,19,Bfor Starfleet Academy. And I-War.      
