OL,3,EWHAT HAPPENED THIS YEAR:GPC ```````````
OL,4,BAll things considered, the PC has      
OL,5,Bprobably had the best line up of games 
OL,6,Bthis year.                             
OL,7,B                                       
OL,8,FIt speaks volumes for the format's new-
OL,9,Ffound versatility that we get real-    
OL,10,Ftime wargames such as Dark Colony side-
OL,11,Fby-side with arcade race 'em ups like  
OL,12,FScreamer Rally, platform shoot 'em ups 
OL,13,Flike Tomb Raider 2 and adventures such 
OL,14,Fas The Curse of Monkey Island.         
OL,16,BHowever, with such a diverse range of  
OL,17,Bproducts, the PC games market has      
OL,18,Bsuffered a number of worrying blips    
OL,19,Bthis year, and sales were erratic.     
