OL,3,ERECOMMENDED GAMES OF 1997:GPC `````````
OL,4,ETOMB RAIDER 2BOh, those levels are so  
OL,5,Bvery, very big.                        
OL,7,EBLADE RUNNERBA game that's different   
OL,8,Bevery time you play it. We've heard it 
OL,9,Bbefore, but this time it works. The    
OL,10,Bfinest movie tie-in of all time.       
OL,12,EOUTLAWSBEveryone but us hated this     
OL,13,Bslightly dated-looking shooter. We     
OL,14,Bdon't care - it's the closest you'll   
OL,15,Bget to Goldeneye on the PC, including  
OL,16,Bthe sniper rifle and train level.      
OL,18,EQUAKE 2BHow much better is the solo    
OL,19,Bplayer mode? Loads better.             
